# sales-point.css

```css
/* RESET */

* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #1d252c;
}

/* PAGE */

.page-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 100vh;
}

/* HEADER */

.header {

    height: 96px;

    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;

    padding-left: 112px;
    padding-right: 112px;

    border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
}

.logo {
    height: 52px;
}

.language-switcher {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
}

.lang {
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    cursor: pointer;

    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
}

.lang.active {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;

    border-radius: 50%;

    background: #154734;
    color: white;
}

/* MAIN LAYOUT */

.content-container {

    display: flex;

    min-height: calc(100vh - 96px);

    width: 100%;
}

/* LEFT SIDE */

.left-panel {

    flex: 1;

    padding-top: 72px;
    padding-left: 112px;
    padding-right: 104px;
}

.left-panel h1 {

    font-size: 64px;
    font-weight: 700;

    line-height: 1.1;

    max-width: 520px;
}

.left-panel h2 {

    margin-top: 16px;

    font-size: 52px;
    font-weight: 300;

    color: #4b5563;
}

.description {

    margin-top: 40px;

    max-width: 520px;

    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1.6;

    color: #5b6470;
}

/* RADIOS */

.radio-group {

    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;

    gap: 18px;

    margin-top: 40px;
}

.radio-group label {

    display: flex;
    align-items: center;

    gap: 12px;

    font-size: 24px;
    color: #444;
}

input[type="radio"] {

    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;

    accent-color: #2f7d32;
}

/* BUTTON */

.confirm-btn {

    margin-top: 40px;

    border: none;

    background: #032d24;
    color: white;

    padding: 16px 36px;

    border-radius: 999px;

    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;

    cursor: pointer;

    transition: all .2s ease;
}

.confirm-btn:hover {
    background: #154734;
}

/* RIGHT SIDE */

.right-panel {

    position: relative;

    width: 600px;
    height: 804px;

    margin: 40px 112px 40px 0;

    overflow: hidden;

    border-top-left-radius: 40px;

    background: #154734;
}

/* GREEN PATTERN */

.pattern-image {

    position: absolute;

    inset: 0;

    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;

    object-fit: cover;
}

/* MASCOT */

.mascot-image {

    position: absolute;

    right: -120px;
    bottom: -140px;

    width: 620px;
    height: auto;

    transform: scaleX(-1);

    z-index: 2;
}

/* TABLET */

@media (max-width: 1200px) {

    .header {
        padding-left: 40px;
        padding-right: 40px;
    }

    .left-panel {
        padding-left: 40px;
        padding-right: 40px;
    }

    .left-panel h1 {
        font-size: 48px;
    }

    .left-panel h2 {
        font-size: 38px;
    }

    .right-panel {
        width: 450px;
        height: 650px;
        margin-right: 40px;
    }
}

/* MOBILE */

@media (max-width: 768px) {

    .header {
        padding: 16px 24px;
    }

    .logo {
        height: 40px;
    }

    .content-container {

        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .left-panel {

        padding: 32px 24px;
        order: 2;
    }

    .right-panel {

        order: 1;

        width: 100%;
        height: 420px;

        margin: 0;

        border-radius: 0;
    }

    .left-panel h1 {
        font-size: 40px;
    }

    .left-panel h2 {
        font-size: 32px;
    }

    .description {
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    .radio-group label {
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    .mascot-image {

        width: 420px;

        right: -80px;
        bottom: -60px;
    }
}
```

### Spring Controller

```java
@Controller
@RequestMapping("/sales-point")
public class SalesPointController {

    @GetMapping
    public String salesPointPage(Model model) {

        return "sales-point";
    }

    @PostMapping
    public String submitSalesPoint(
            @RequestParam String salesPoint) {

        System.out.println("Selected: " + salesPoint);

        return "redirect:/next-page";
    }
}
```

This version is:

* ✅ Thymeleaf compatible
* ✅ Mobile responsive
* ✅ Uses the exact two-panel layout from Figma
* ✅ Separate background pattern and mascot images
* ✅ Mascot mirrored (`scaleX(-1)`)
* ✅ Easy to connect to your Arthur Core sales point flow later.
